ts 3-5 years of banking experience Bachelor's degree in Finance, Business, or Economics Knowledge of banking regulations Excellent verbal and written communication skills Excellent analytical skills Develop rapport with customers Branch Manager related job titles: Bank Manager Assistant Branch Manager Commercial Banking Manager Banking Manager Assistant Commercial Banking Manager Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
